<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></span><br>Still interested in a Kingsbridge insurance policy?<br><br>Renew within the next 7 days and we'll send you £40 in&nbsp;<a href="https://www.voucherexpress.co.uk/full-range.aspx">online vouchers</a>.<br><br>Call&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;to purchase over the phone.&nbsp;Alternatively, buy your business insurance policy&nbsp;<a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/buy?journey=1">online</a>.<br><span style="background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br>Sales Team<br><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br>T:&nbsp;01242 808740<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><br><b><font size="1">Offer Terms and Conditions:<br></font></b></span><font size="1"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">1. This offer is valid only to Kingsbridge customers who renew a Professional Indemnity or Public Liability package and excludes the purchase of Legal Expenses and IR35 Protect policies purchased on their own.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">2. The policy must be purchased within 7 days of the offer being communicated by Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">3. This offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other Kingsbridge voucher offer.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">4. Online vouchers will be sent 28 days after the policy start date and a 6-month validity period will apply. Vouchers may take between 7-10 days to reach customers. Online vouchers can be redeemed for a gift card of the customer’s choice at Voucher Express from a range of Vendors. Full range for the VEX Multi-Choice voucher can be viewed&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.voucherexpress.co.uk/full-range.aspx" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">here</a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">5. Rewards are subject to availability.</span></font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
